These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: potato, cauliflower, strawberry, tomato
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, hip-hop, rock, soul
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, egyptian, indonesian, spanish
4 different pets are kept: fish, cat, lizard, goat
 1. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 2. the person eating potato is in an even position##4
 3. the japanese is on the left of the fan of rock##1
 4. the indonesian is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
 5. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
 6. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
 7. the egyptian is the person eating strawberry##1
 8. the owner of the lizard is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the goat and the fan of soul##2
10. the person eating potato is the owner of the goat##1
11. the fan of rock is the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | strawberry  | potato    | tomato    | cauliflower   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop     | folk   | rock       | soul    |
| Nationality   | egyptian | japanese | spanish    | indonesian |
| Pet           | cat | goat       | fish | lizard     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, peach, tomato, grapefruit
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, cooking, magic-tricks, skydiving
There are 4 different nationalities: french, canadian, chinese, russian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, weightlifting, lacrosse, water-polo
 1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4
 2. the canadian is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
 4. the person eating peach is the french##1
 5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
 6. the french is on the left or right of the chinese##3
 7. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
 8. the russian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 9. the chinese is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating tomato is in an odd position##4
11. the chinese is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Food          | cranberry  | peach    | tomato     | grapefruit       |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | skydiving | card-games   | cooking |
| Nationality   | chinese | french   | canadian   | russian    |
| Sport         | lacrosse | water-polo  | ice-hockey | weightlifting   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, 7up, coffee
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, police-officer, bartender, analyst
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, turkish, mexican, chinese
4 different pets are kept: rat, hamster, bird, goldfish
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the videographer##3
 2. the turkish is the bartender##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 4. the videographer is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 5. the person drinking tea is the analyst##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 7. the owner of the rat is the chinese##1
 8. the analyst is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the thai##1
10. the owner of the rat is the person drinking 7up##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | 7up   | coffee    | tea      |
| Job           | bartender | videographer | police-officer | analyst     |
| Nationality   | turkish      | chinese   | thai   | mexican |
| Pet           | goldfish         | rat       | bird  | hamster       |

