.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk, almond-milk, hot-chocolate
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, grapefruit, cucumber, cauliflower
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, traveling, magic-tricks, gardening
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, water-polo, climbing, snowboarding
 1. the person drinking 7up is the person eating cranberry##1
 2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 3. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
 4. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking milk is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 8. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
 9. the person who's sport is climbing is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
10. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating cauliflower##1
12. the person eating cauliflower is on the left or right of the person eating cranberry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate       | almond-milk   | 7up   | milk   |
| Food       | grapefruit        | cauliflower | cranberry    | cucumber       |
| Hobby      | gardening | traveling    | magic-tricks  | dancing |
| Sport      | water-polo  | climbing  | badminton | snowboarding    |

