.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, corn, eggplant, plum
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, skydiving, drawing, photography
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, dancer, doctor, entrepreneur
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, golf, skateboarding, rowing
 1. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person eating plum##2
 3. the doctor is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
 4. the dancer is the person eating pomegranate##1
 5. the project-manager is on the left or right of the dancer##3
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating corn is the project-manager##1
 8. the person who's hobby is drawing is the dancer##1
 9. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
10. the dancer is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
11. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
12. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Food    | eggplant    | plum      | pomegranate          | corn    |
| Hobby   | skydiving | photography       | drawing | collecting |
| Job     | entrepreneur     | doctor      | dancer     | project-manager |
| Sport   | golf   | rowing | skateboarding        | lacrosse   |

