.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, almond-milk, soy-milk, hot-chocolate
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, garlic, asparagus, plum
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, trance, reggae, blues
There are 4 different nationalities: british, japanese, polish, australian
 1. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 2. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 3. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 5. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan of blues is between the polish and the fan of trance##2
 7. the fan of reggae is the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating asparagus##1
 9. the japanese is on the far right##1
10. the british is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk  | almond-milk    | sprite       | hot-chocolate       |
| Food          | plum    | asparagus | garlic | pumpkin     |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | reggae        | blues    | trance   |
| Nationality   | british  | polish      | australian    | japanese |

