There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, russian, brazilian, malaysian
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, rat, mouse, guinea-pig
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, helicopter, taxi, bus
 1. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 2. the malaysian is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 3. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 4. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the turkish##3
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 6. the brazilian is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 7. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 8. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
 9. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
10. the russian is on the far right##1
11. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
12. the owner of the rabbit is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | musical    | adventure  | family      |
| Nationality   | turkish      | brazilian | malaysian | russian   |
