 7. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the polish##1
 9. the owner of the goat is between the indonesian and the person watching documentary movies##2
10. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
11. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an even position##4
12. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3

