The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, romance, superhero, epic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, hip-hop, metal, rock
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, baseball, skateboarding, handball
 1. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the fan of rock##1
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4
 3. the fan of disco is between the person watching romance movies and the person who's sport is baseball##2
 4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
 5. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
 6. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
 7. the fan of rock is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's sport is handball is the person watching romance movies##1
 9. the person eating cauliflower is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
11. the person eating cauliflower is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
13. the fan of metal is on the right of the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| Food          | cauliflower     | raspberry      | papaya  | nectarine        |
| Movie-Genre   | romance     | superhero | animation | epic      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop      | disco        | rock        | metal        |
| Sport         | handball | tennis    | baseball      | skateboarding |

