The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, skateboard, ship, bike
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
 2. the person eating peach is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
 4. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 5. the person driving the ship is in an odd position##4
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is the person driving the airplane##1
 7. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 8. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 9. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
10. the person eating peach is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
11. the person eating spinach is on the far left##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2    |     3     |       4       |
