 3. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the nurse##3
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person who's hobby is reading and the firefighter##2
 5. the person eating lime is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 6. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an odd position##4
 7. the person eating peas is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the librarian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
 9. the person eating apricot is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's sport is skiing is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
11. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left or far right##3
12. the nurse is on the left or right of the librarian##3
13. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |   3    |     4      |
