.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola, sprite, coffee
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, camping, sudoku, board-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, epic, romance, documentary
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, biathlon, lacrosse, climbing
 1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
 2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 3. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 4. the person watching epic movies is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 7. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
11. the person watching documentary movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | sprite       | cola | fanta        | coffee        |
| Hobby         | board-games | sudoku       | drawing | camping |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary     | epic        | family    | romance      |
| Sport         | biathlon     | lacrosse    | climbing | cricket   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, folk, country, d&b
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, pakistani, italian, british
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, baseball, skateboarding, rowing
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, airplane, scooter, quad-bike
 1. the fan of d&b is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the canadian and the british##2
 3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
 4. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the pakistani##1
 5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 6. the fan of folk is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
 8. the british is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
10. the canadian is in an even position##4
11. the canadian is on the far right##1
12. the fan of r&b is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | folk      | r&b | d&b     | country        |
| Nationality   | italian | british  | pakistani     | canadian |
| Sport         | baseball    | weightlifting | skateboarding      | rowing |
| Transport     | quad-bike | airplane     | scooter | bus       |

 